Senior Project Experience with a major Senior Paper  6 hours  Two electives from International Studies  9 hours  Three electives from departments other than International Studies to include History  Economics  Engineering  Math and Sciences   Back to Top   Print Degree Planner   Print Friendly Page   All catalogues   2016 Virginia Military Institute  Powered by the Acalog  Academic Catalog Management System   ACMS  Mobile Site 